Class AbstractProtocolTransport

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.james.protocols.api.AbstractProtocolTransport
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ProtocolTransport
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    NettyProtocolTransport

    public abstract class AbstractProtocolTransport
extends Object
implements ProtocolTransport
    Abstract base class for ProtocolTransport implementation which already takes care of all the complex stuff when handling Response's.
